snippet.title: Horses - Official Announcement Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2023
snippet.description:
Horses, a deeply creepy first-person adventure game where you take on the role of a summer worker on a farm featuring some troubling livestock. The player will have a chance to obey the farmer's cryptic rules or go his own way and try to uncover hidden secrets. To be honest, we have no idea what we're in for on this one, but it looks insane and we're here for it.

Check out more at https://horses.wtf

#SummerOfGaming #IGN
